<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Elizabeth Gillies, 27, married Michael Corcoran, 47, months after postponing their wedding due to the ongoing pandemic.</p>

<p>The Dynasty actress shared the news of her gorgeous nuptials to Vogue on Wednesday and released a few photos byÂ photographer Emily LipsonÂ from the big day on Instagram.</p>

<p>Gillies and Corcoran, who had been dating for six years, said 'I do' at the Inn at Fernbrook Farms in New Jersey with a small group of friends and family to witness their union.</p>

