<p>The ceremony was planned in one month and Elizabeth's father served as their officiant.</p>

<p>'It has been such a long road for us, and at times [it] felt like a total impossibility that it was hard to believe we'd actually gotten to that moment where it was really happening,' Gillies said.Â </p>

<p>'Once we were exchanging vows, it hit me that my dad was marrying us and our loved ones were there, and I think I turned to Michael and mouthed, "Oh, my God, we actually did it." We were so happy.'Â Â </p>
